Tickets for this flight can be purchased by contacting the Lao Airlines Call Centre on 1626 or via Ticket Lao +856 (0)20 5255 8787 and other Lao Airlines Agencies
24 June 2021 to Incheon with Lao Airlines
Tickets for this flights can be purchased by contacting the Lao Airlines Call Centre on 1626 or via Ticket Lao +856 (0)20 5255 8787 and other Lao Airlines Agencies
A number of commercial flight options are appearing on airline sites. You should consider existing entry / transit regulations carefully before booking flights, including restrictions on foreigners entering or transiting. You should consult FCDO Travel Advice in the first instance.
Lao Government COVID-19 regulations require that you inform the Embassy if you’re departing Laos.
Email BritishEmbassy.Vientiane@fcdo.gov.uk with your full name, passport number, flight details and a scan or photograph of the identification page of your passport.
The Embassy will inform the Lao Ministry of Foreign Affairs of departing British nationals as required by the Lao government.
Further information
The British Embassy Vientiane will also issue urgent updates on the UKinLaos Facebook page.
